Package org.netbeans.spi.java.project.support

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtraSourceJavadocSupport
    Utility factory class for ant-based project implementors, the created instances, once put into project's lookup, make sure the javadoc and source references in project properties are correctly recognized and used by the java infrastructure.
    JavadocAndSourceRootDetection
    Miscellaneous helper utils to detect Javadoc root folder, source root folder or package of the given java or class file.
    LookupMergerSupport
    Factory class for creation of LookupMerger instances.
    PreferredProjectPlatform
    Returns a preferred JavaPlatform for a new project.
    ProjectPlatform
    A factory for transient JavaPlatform defined within a project.
